task.summary: Added a few semicolons, and set up to work on my machine

Created minimum-viable product login page. Added a basic NavBar, Login, and LoginContainer component. Most of these components are simply display components, with later refactoring to include more functionality. The 'Sign in with Google' button works for now.
Fixed the cookies issue so now /getUser route works.
Set it up so it now currUser reducer is null if no user is logged in, or contains a user object if the user is logged in.
